high_descs: Walk forward to the tennis racket on the floor.
Pick up the tennis racket from beside the plant.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk across the room to the desk.
Turn on the lamp on the left side of the desk.
anns.task_desc: To see the racket in the light.

high_descs: Move forward to the racket on the floor.
Pick up the racket on the floor.
Turn around and bring the racket to the desk with the lamp.
Turn on the lamp on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Examine a racket in the light of the lamp.

high_descs: Take a small step to the right then go straight until you are next to the wall.
Pick up the tennis racket off the floor that is next to the plant.
Turn around then head straight until you reach the small table, then turn right and head straight and turn left then right so you are in front of the left side of the desk.
Turn on the lamp that is on the desk next to the alarm clock.
anns.task_desc: Turn on a lamp while holding a tennis racket.
